flowchart TD
  A[Checkout repo] --> B[Install toolchain (nasm, build-essential)]
  B --> C[Build (make -f build/makefile)]
  C --> D[Run tests (tests/run_tests.sh)]
  D --> E{Tests pass?}
  E -- yes --> F[Package artifacts]
  F --> G[Create GitHub Release (attach artifacts)]
  E -- no --> H[Fail CI / notify]
